hopobject.body: How would you like the money? testosterone overdose They'll continue to co-star as an on-screen couple for "Vampire Diaries," but the life's been sucked out of Nina Dobrev and Ian Somerhalder's relationship. After more than three years of dating, the on-screen and real-life couple have parted ways, according to an Us Weekly report. The two first went public with their romance in 2011 and "will continue to work together and remain best friends, which is where the relationship started," a source told the magazine.
